==Equipment==
The boss has -2 [[flat armour]] and is weak to crush, so it is recommended to use a crush weapon that deals damage with multiple hitsplats such as the [[Scythe of vitur|scythe of Vitur]], [[dual macuahuitl]], or [[glacial temotli]]. [[Torag's hammers]] are not recommended, as their slower attack speed means that they perform worse than a [[dragon mace]] and [[dragon defender]], assuming all other gear is equivalent.

Given the relatively low defence of the boss, strength bonus should be prioritised.

Although the boss has a 30% [[elemental weakness]] to fire, it is better to take melee as the [[unstable ice]]  can only take damage from melee sources. This means taking [[Thrall|thralls]] is recommended.

